Don't do this to me.

1402
01:16:32,553 --> 01:16:35,763
- You can make me do it, but
you can't make me act in it.

1403
01:16:35,798 --> 01:16:38,041
I'll be unprepared, I'll be late.

1404
01:16:38,076 --> 01:16:41,010
- I think you're too much
the professional for that.

1405
01:16:41,044 --> 01:16:42,390
- In a pig's eye.

1406
01:16:57,923 --> 01:16:59,545
But I want Eddie there.

1407
01:16:59,580 --> 01:17:00,685
- Well of course.

1408
01:17:00,719 --> 01:17:03,170
- To play the role of Steve.

1409
01:17:03,204 --> 01:17:04,171
- What?

1410
01:17:04,205 --> 01:17:05,206
He's a singer!

1411
01:17:05,241 --> 01:17:06,380
- Singing is acting.

1412
01:17:06,414 --> 01:17:09,555
He's acted in front of
hundreds, thousands of people.

1413
01:17:09,590 --> 01:17:11,937
He's perfect for the role.

1414
01:17:11,972 --> 01:17:14,077
Do this for me, please.

1415
