You really are mad at me this morning.

1416
01:17:36,444 --> 01:17:38,101
- Put your coat on!

1417
01:17:40,586 --> 01:17:41,933
- Why this morning?

1418
01:17:43,175 --> 01:17:45,937
- Because I'm sick of opening
this door every other day

1419
01:17:45,971 --> 01:17:49,941
and finding you burned
out, boozed up, and...

1420
01:17:52,598 --> 01:17:55,118
