1421
01:17:56,568 --> 01:17:57,396
Sorry, baby.

1422
01:17:58,466 --> 01:18:00,641
- [sighs] Eddie, you're not even trying.

1423
01:18:00,676 --> 01:18:02,747
We broke early so that you could rehearse.

1424
01:18:02,781 --> 01:18:03,609
- I am trying!

1425
01:18:03,644 --> 01:18:04,990
I never said I was an actor.

1426
01:18:05,025 --> 01:18:06,164
- No, I did.

1427
01:18:06,198 --> 01:18:08,822
And what this hateful film
doesn't destroy, you will.

1428
01:18:08,856 --> 01:18:10,962
I staked my reputation on you.

1429
01:18:10,996 --> 01:18:12,377
- Did I ask for this?

1430
01:18:12,411 --> 01:18:14,275
Did I ever ask to be in this?

1431
01:18:14,310 --> 01:18:15,518
- No, you don't ask.

1432
01:18:15,552 --> 01:18:19,073
You just sit around waiting
for Mama to make it better.

1433
01:18:19,108 --> 01:18:19,971
- Hey hey hey.

1434
01:18:20,005 --> 01:18:22,456
Come on you two, you don't wanna do this.

1435
01:18:22,490 --> 01:18:23,319
- I do.

1436
01:18:23,353 --> 01:18:24,458
I want to kill something.

1437
01:18:24,492 --> 01:18:25,873
- No no, Bessie Mae.

1438
01:18:25,908 --> 01:18:29,981
Come on, go get dressed, we
have reservations at eight.

1439
01:18:30,015 --> 01:18:30,878
Go on.

1440
01:18:32,915 --> 01:18:34,433
Eddie, come here.

1441
01:18:35,952 --> 01:18:38,265
It's all right, come here.

1442
01:18:39,300 --> 01:18:41,268
Now look, you can't just say the words.

1443
01:18:41,302 --> 01:18:42,303
- You're telling me.

1444
01:18:42,338 --> 01:18:45,203
- No no, I mean you gotta
feel past the words.

1445
01:18:45,237 --> 01:18:49,000
They're nothing, an envelope, maybe.

1446
01:18:49,034 --> 01:18:52,279
The message comes from here, the gut.

1447
01:18:54,384 --> 01:18:55,454
- Sure.

1448
01:18:55,489 --> 01:18:57,525
- Okay, over here, come on.

1449
01:18:57,560 --> 01:18:58,941
This guy Steve.

1450
01:18:59,976 --> 01:19:02,565
He looks at this woman, he's had her.

1451
01:19:02,599 --> 01:19:03,773
Right?

1452
01:19:03,808 --> 01:19:06,914
And he looks at her and
he sees filth, dirt.

1453
01:19:06,949 --> 01:19:10,815
You have to look at
Elizabeth and see filth.

1454
01:19:10,849 --> 01:19:12,333
- But I love her.

1455
01:19:12,368 --> 01:19:13,231
- Now.

1456
01:19:13,265 --> 01:19:16,199
Now come on, pal, you can do it, come on.

1457
01:19:16,234 --> 01:19:19,478
Come on, from the gut, you can do it.

1458
01:19:25,864 --> 01:19:29,834
- I'm sick of opening that door every.

1459
01:19:29,868 --> 01:19:31,697
I'm sick of...

1460
