crazed and wonderful chap,

1863
01:38:38,360 --> 01:38:39,499
named Faustus.

1864
01:38:41,053 --> 01:38:42,847
- Crazed and wonderful?

1865
01:38:42,882 --> 01:38:44,539
- Oh yes, brilliant fellow,

1866
01:38:44,573 --> 01:38:45,643
but poor sod,

1867
01:38:47,093 --> 01:38:49,716
sold his soul to the devil.

1868
01:38:49,751 --> 01:38:50,441
- Why?

1869
01:38:50,476 --> 01:38:51,615
- Why?

1870
01:38:51,649 --> 01:38:54,894
For the love of the most
beautiful woman in the world,

1871
01:38:54,929 --> 01:38:56,309
of course.

1872
01:38:56,344 --> 01:38:57,138
- Hmm.

1873
01:38:57,172 --> 01:39:00,141
Doesn't sound so brilliant to me.

1874
01:39:00,831 --> 01:39:04,662
