1885
01:39:49,224 --> 01:39:50,674
- Oh, I sincerely hope so.

1886
01:39:50,708 --> 01:39:53,056
Not one single paparazzi in sight.

1887
01:39:53,090 --> 01:39:54,712
- How do I look?

1888
01:39:54,747 --> 01:39:56,059
- [laughs]

1889
01:39:56,093 --> 01:39:57,750
Ridiculous.

1890
01:39:57,784 --> 01:39:59,096
- At least no-one will spot me.

1891
01:39:59,131 --> 01:40:00,477
- Spot you?

1892
01:40:00,511 --> 01:40:02,858
You like you're wearing a
bloody marshmallow on your head.

1893
01:40:02,893 --> 01:40:03,756
Ow!

1894
01:40:05,378 --> 01:40:08,036
[music swells]

1895
01:40:13,766 --> 01:40:16,493
[birds tweet]

1896
01:40:16,527 --> 01:40:17,494
At last,

1897
01:40:17,528 --> 01:40:19,461
we seem to have thrown off the shameless

1898
01:40:19,496 --> 01:40:23,569
shackles of fame and shuffled
off that mortal coil.

1899
01:40:23,603 --> 01:40:25,260
- It's amazing.

1900
01:40:25,295 --> 01:40:27,090
They were looking for
Elizabeth Taylor in Rome,

1901
01:40:27,124 --> 01:40:28,884
and we left her there.

1902
01:40:28,919 --> 01:40:31,542
[laughs]

1903
01:40:31,577 --> 01:40:33,510
- I suppose it will be a bit of cliche to

1904
