Flaws and all?

1946
01:41:58,008 --> 01:41:59,389
- [scoffs]

1947
01:41:59,423 --> 01:42:00,286
Flaws?

1948
01:42:02,978 --> 01:42:05,291
Flaws, yes, I do want you.

1949
01:42:07,293 --> 01:42:08,950
You're a deep, vast,

1950
01:42:08,984 --> 01:42:10,779
[slow emotional music]

1951
01:42:10,814 --> 01:42:11,918
terrifying ocean,

1952
01:42:11,953 --> 01:42:13,541
and I do think ...

1953
