1975
01:43:54,918 --> 01:43:56,713
- Mm, where does the time go?

1976
01:43:56,747 --> 01:43:58,404
- Oh, I wonder.

1977
01:43:58,439 --> 01:43:59,440
Hmm.

1978
01:43:59,474 --> 01:44:00,751
You were rather a bit
of a mess this morning

