01:44:21,151 --> 01:44:22,394
It was lust.

1992
01:44:22,428 --> 01:44:24,154
- Love, you bloated old goat!

1993
01:44:24,188 --> 01:44:24,948
Love!

1994
01:44:24,982 --> 01:44:26,121
- You silly trollop!

1995
01:44:26,156 --> 01:44:28,434
