Everything but the lines.

2013
01:45:05,747 --> 01:45:07,231
- All right, places everybody!

2014
01:45:07,266 --> 01:45:09,233
- Elizabeth, you look radiant, my darling!

2015
01:45:09,268 --> 01:45:10,442
Mmm.

2016
01:45:10,476 --> 01:45:12,858
The sunshine of our day!

2017
01:45:12,892 --> 01:45:13,859
Come, let me show you.

2018
01:45:13,893 --> 01:45:14,722
Richard?

2019
