[men shout]

2023
01:45:35,052 --> 01:45:38,193
[slow Mediterranean music]

2024
01:45:38,228 --> 01:45:42,025
[speaks in foreign language]

2025
01:45:46,512 --> 01:45:47,962
- Where's Eddie?

2026
01:45:56,211 --> 01:45:57,074
Eddie?

2027
01:45:59,387 --> 01:46:00,354
We're about to sit down,

2028
01:46:00,388 --> 01:46:01,872
what's going on?

2029
01:46:01,907 --> 01:46:03,046
- Socks.

2030
01:46:03,080 --> 01:46:03,943
Underwear.

2031
01:46:04,634 --> 01:46:06,463
- Eddie, stop this!

2032
01:46:07,257 --> 01:46:08,569
- Look,

2033
01:46:08,603 --> 01:46:10,674
I'm not going away for good,
so don't go nuts, okay?

2034
