01:47:21,400 --> 01:47:22,781
- I am in love!

2074
01:47:24,990 --> 01:47:26,060
With this girl.

2075
01:47:26,094 --> 01:47:28,027
- You have your own girl.

2076
01:47:28,062 --> 01:47:29,201
You have Sybil.

2077
01:47:29,235 --> 01:47:30,098
- Sybil.

2078
01:47:31,306 --> 01:47:32,618
And Elizabeth

2079
01:47:32,653 --> 01:47:34,240
