2080
01:47:42,007 --> 01:47:42,870
You are

2081
01:47:44,147 --> 01:47:45,873
my girl, aren't you?

2082
01:47:47,461 --> 01:47:50,256
[slow sad music]

2083
01:47:51,257 --> 01:47:52,120
- Yes.

2084
01:47:54,364 --> 01:47:55,883
- You're my girl.

2085
01:47:57,298 --> 01:47:58,955
Come here.

2086
01:47:58,989 --> 01:47:59,990
And kiss me.

2087
01:48:02,096 --> 01:48:05,479
[music builds concern]

2088
01:48:24,877 --> 01:48:28,294
