01:48:51,179 --> 01:48:52,180
I know that,

2099
01:48:53,699 --> 01:48:54,942
that it will soon be dawn,

2100
01:48:54,976 --> 01:48:57,082
and in that harsh light,
my thoughts will clear

2101
01:48:57,116 --> 01:49:00,223
and I will, I will rescue my Guinevere,

2102
01:49:00,257 --> 01:49:02,984
I will do the right thing, I ...

2103
