02:02:52,813 --> 02:02:55,298
- But you must promise me something.

2416
02:02:55,333 --> 02:02:58,854
You must promise never to think bad of me.

2417
02:02:58,888 --> 02:02:59,717
- Never.

2418
02:03:00,545 --> 02:03:03,962
Never, not one single bad thought in

2419
02:03:03,997 --> 02:03:06,448
this old drunken Welsh head.

2420
02:03:07,966 --> 02:03:09,554
Not for Elizabeth.

2421
02:03:11,418 --> 02:03:12,833
- Promise?

2422
02:03:12,868 --> 02:03:14,179
- Yes.

2423
02:03:14,214 --> 02:03:16,803
