2438
02:04:07,336 --> 02:04:08,820
- They're saying you sold out, Rich.

2439
02:04:08,855 --> 02:04:10,304
- Yes.

2440
02:04:10,339 --> 02:04:11,858
I am old Faustus.

2441
02:04:14,654 --> 02:04:16,725
Or the latter day Faust.

2442
02:04:16,759 --> 02:04:20,107
Got a three picture deal
