02:07:48,143 --> 02:07:50,801
[siren blares]

2523
02:08:01,570 --> 02:08:05,194
- It's after four, I was concerned.

2524
02:08:05,229 --> 02:08:06,955
How did she take it?

2525
02:08:08,991 --> 02:08:10,613
Sybil, what did she say?

2526
02:08:10,648 --> 02:08:11,753
- Not much.

2527
02:08:13,202 --> 02:08:14,238
- You told her?

2528
02:08:14,272 --> 02:08:15,135
- No.

2529
02:08:16,102 --> 02:08:17,241
[laughs]

2530
02:08:17,275 --> 02:08:18,138
Oh.

2531
02:08:20,106 --> 02:08:24,144
No reproaches, no rampage,
no threats of death

2532
02:08:25,870 --> 02:08:28,355
and destruction, Richard you fool,

2533
02:08:28,390 --> 02:08:32,049
Richard you lout, you
