2534
02:08:32,083 --> 02:08:34,637
[groans]

2535
02:08:34,672 --> 02:08:36,501
Where the hell you think you're going?

2536
02:08:36,536 --> 02:08:37,917
- I'm going to my room,

2537
02:08:37,951 --> 02:08:39,504
and you're going home to Sybil.

2538
02:08:39,539 --> 02:08:40,609
- To hell I am.

2539
02:08:40,643 --> 02:08:42,024
I'm coming through that door.

2540
02:08:42,059 --> 02:08:44,268
- Well, you better bring a locksmith.

2541
02:08:44,302 --> 02:08:48,341
- You can't toss me out
like some errant schoolboy!

2542
02:08:48,375 --> 02:08:50,619
- Richard, you can have
a wife and a mistress,

2543
