2544
02:08:53,691 --> 02:08:54,692
- Why not?

2545
02:08:54,727 --> 02:08:55,658
- Because,

2546
02:08:55,693 --> 02:08:57,074
I'm the fiance.

2547
02:09:00,111 --> 02:09:01,630
[door slams]

2548
02:09:01,664 --> 02:09:02,942
- You think just because I'm drunk

2549
02:09:02,976 --> 02:09:05,116
I'm not gonna remember any
of this in the morning,

2550
02:09:05,151 --> 02:09:06,014
you cow!

2551
02:09:07,291 --> 02:09:09,327
[yells]

2552
02:09:09,362 --> 02:09:10,225
You sow!

2553
02:09:24,135 --> 02:09:26,137
[dials]

2554
02:09:30,486 --> 02:09:33,524
[swigs bottle]

2555
02:09:33,558 --> 02:09:36,285
[cars drive by]

2556
02:09:38,253 --> 02:09:40,669
[sighs]

2557
02:09:40,703 --> 02:09:42,291
Sybil, hello love.

2558
02:09:43,776 --> 02:09:47,055
Yes, yes, I know it's rather late.

2559
02:09:47,089 --> 02:09:51,404
Well, it's early actually [laughs].

2560
02:09:51,438 --> 02:09:53,578
No, no, I didn't tell her.

2561
02:09:55,028 --> 02:09:57,203
Well, the thing is love,

2562
02:09:58,273 --> 02:10:01,966
I do believe I'm going to need a divorce.

2563
02:10:09,802 --> 02:10:12,977
[puts phone down]

2564
02:10:13,012 --> 02:10:15,497
[police siren blares]

2565
02:10:15,531 --> 02:10:17,533
[blows whistle]

2566
02:10:17,568 --> 02:10:20,295
[crowd yells]

2567
02:10:20,329 --> 02:10:23,194
- This is like being
swallowed up by an avalanche.

2568
02:10:23,229 --> 02:10:25,334
- Yes, every night the same thing,

2569
02:10:25,369 --> 02:10:26,888
more of these ...

2570
02:10:28,199 --> 02:10:28,993
- Vultures!

2571
02:10:29,028 --> 02:10:30,823
- No fans, love, fans.

2572
02:10:30,857 --> 02:10:32,997
All come to see me, me.

2573
02:10:33,032 --> 02:10:34,447
- Love, they come to see us,

2574
02:10:34,481 --> 02:10:36,759
we're a pair of circus freaks.

2575
02:10:36,794 --> 02:10:38,175
Well it's true, the
only reason they're here

2576
02:10:38,209 --> 02:10:40,142
