2577
02:10:40,177 --> 02:10:43,974
[crowd cheers and applaud]

2578
02:10:58,712 --> 02:11:01,439
[crowd applaud]

2579
02:11:17,386 --> 02:11:19,078
- That man is a child of the theater.

2580
02:11:19,112 --> 02:11:21,839
- Mmm, just a natural chic bea.

2581
02:11:21,874 --> 02:11:24,048
It's where he belongs.

2582
02:11:24,083 --> 02:11:26,119
- You wouldn't mind if he stayed?

2583
02:11:26,154 --> 02:11:29,122
- I just want to be with Richard.

2584
02:11:31,055 --> 02:11:33,333
- Congratulations.

2585
02:11:33,368 --> 02:11:36,095
[crowd applaud]

2586
02:11:47,900 --> 02:11:49,177
- Thank you.

2587
02:11:49,211 --> 02:11:51,800
You're such a kind audience,

2588
02:11:51,834 --> 02:11:53,422
all of you.

2589
02:11:53,457 --> 02:11:54,320
However,

2590
02:11:55,355 --> 02:11:58,531
my heart feels either appreciations,

2591
02:11:59,773 --> 02:12:02,500
I have at last married the girl.

2592
02:12:05,020 --> 02:12:08,161
[crowd applaud]

2593
02:12:08,196 --> 02:12:11,233
And indeed, she is such a treasure

2594
02:12:12,579 --> 02:12:14,443
that I must honor her.

2595
02:12:15,479 --> 02:12:18,068
[crowd cheer]

2596
02:12:18,827 --> 02:12:19,690
My bride.

2597
02:12:24,005 --> 02:12:26,007
You see, they love us.

2598
02:12:26,835 --> 02:12:28,423
- Mmm, please don't turn your back,

2599
02:12:28,457 --> 02:12:32,945
they love the lions as much
as they love the Christians.

2600
02:12:35,844 --> 02:12:37,708
- Ladies and gentlemen,

2601
02:12:37,742 --> 02:12:40,193
as the bard would have it,

2602
02:12:40,228 --> 02:12:43,610
we will have no more marriages.

2603
02:12:43,645 --> 02:12:45,509
[laughs]

2604
02:12:45,543 --> 02:12:48,270
[crowd applaud]

2605
02:12:54,656 --> 02:12:55,588
[birds tweet]

2606
02:12:55,622 --> 02:12:57,866
- So you've both
undergone a lot of changes

2607
02:12:57,900 --> 02:12:59,972
to play in Virginia Woolf.

