Richard doesn't let me use
four letter words at home.

2615
02:13:17,644 --> 02:13:19,336
- Yes, I've cured Elizabeth of

2616
02:13:19,370 --> 02:13:21,683
that rather unfortunate tendency.

2617
02:13:21,717 --> 02:13:23,133
- You bet your ass.

2618
02:13:23,167 --> 02:13:25,687
- That's a three letter word.

2619
02:13:27,723 --> 02:13:29,829
Of course my only concern
is that my quality

2620
02:13:29,863 --> 02:13:33,212
is not exactly this American professor

2621
02:13:33,246 --> 02:13:35,766
I've gone to see, he's not ...

2622
02:13:35,800 --> 02:13:36,974
- Rich?

2623
02:13:37,009 --> 02:13:39,632
- He's not me, this moon-faced chap,

2624
02:13:39,666 --> 02:13:41,979
beaten down by a woman.

2625
02:13:42,014 --> 02:13:43,049
- Richard!

2626
02:13:51,057 --> 02:13:52,817
- Thank you, Mr Burton.

2627
02:13:52,852 --> 02:13:55,165
[Richard mumbles]

2628
02:13:55,199 --> 02:13:56,614
- You're mumbling!

2629
02:13:56,649 --> 02:13:58,892
- I'm running my lines.

2630
02:13:58,927 --> 02:13:59,652
- Mumbler!

2631
02:14:00,756 --> 02:14:03,276
- One of your less glaring
defects, Elizabeth,

2632
02:14:03,311 --> 02:14:05,244
is you've never been able to distinguish

2633
02:14:05,278 --> 02:14:07,453
