2634
02:14:09,386 --> 02:14:10,421
- Can too.

2635
02:14:10,456 --> 02:14:11,802
You're a mumbler!

2636
02:14:12,699 --> 02:14:14,460
Accurate lines?

2637
02:14:14,494 --> 02:14:18,360
