George takes the bottle,

2638
02:14:18,395 --> 02:14:19,258
and pours.

2639
02:14:19,844 --> 02:14:21,087
[pours]

2640
02:14:21,122 --> 02:14:22,364
- Don't you think you've
rehearsed that one enough?

2641
02:14:22,399 --> 02:14:23,710
- Oh, it's method, darling.

2642
02:14:23,745 --> 02:14:26,506
You see, I'm sending my way
into the role of a drunk.

2643
02:14:26,541 --> 02:14:28,301
- Hah, for years!

