02:15:26,221 --> 02:15:30,156
- Take to the Russians
take to the magic of vodka.

2670
02:15:30,191 --> 02:15:32,193
I'm a vegetarian.

2671
02:15:32,227 --> 02:15:34,574
- I'm speechless.

2672
02:15:34,609 --> 02:15:35,541
- Oh, I hope not,

2673
02:15:35,575 --> 02:15:37,370
I'd miss your voice, my little dove.

2674
02:15:37,405 --> 02:15:39,200
- You'd be thrilled.

